  "title": "Sales Coordinator #82056",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Distributor - piping</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales Coordinator</strong></li><li>Working Location: Woodlands</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon to Fri: 9:00am to 6:00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Process and follow up on customer sales orders and quotations</li><li>Coordinate with procurement, logistics, and warehouse teams to ensure smooth order fulfillment</li><li>Update customers on order status, delivery timelines, and stock availability</li><li>Maintain accurate sales records and documents in the system</li><li>Respond to customer enquiries and provide basic product/technical support (training provided)</li><li>Prepare simple sales reports and support inventory tracking when needed</li><li>Provide administrative support to the sales team and assist with internal coordination</li><li>Ensure all sales activities follow company procedures and customer service standards</li><li>Handle ad-hoc tasks and special projects as assigned</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum O-Levels.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office, especially Excel.</li><li>Experience with Microsoft Dynamics NAV is a plus.</li><li>Candidates without relevant experience are welcome to apply; training will be provided.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#82056 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
